	<plot>This volume of Hudson Best Collection brings two classic Famicom action games to your GameBoy Advance:1. Challenger2. Milon's Secret CastleCheat: At the very start of stage 1, at the top of the train, wait for the timer to go 87 seconds. When you hear a "kan kan" or "tan tan"-like sound (2 quick high notes), throw a dagger on your left. Do this 4 times. The invulnerability will be activated when a bonus score is displayed. The invulnerability lasts only for stage 1.Cheat: Beat the game 2 times in a row to get the Secret Ending Message.  The Secret Ending Message says:  "This is the end of Episode 1.  See you again!"</plot>
